Have you switched to MCI Mail lately? If so, contact Amy Gahran, 
who is trying to track down an SEJ listserv problem. An as-yet-
unknown subscriber to the listserv switched to MCI Mail from 
another service, and arranged to have e-mail forwarded to the new 
MCI Mail address. Something malfunctioned, and 
0002587301@mcimail.com has been receiving that member's 
SEJlistserv e-mail. If this sounds like it may apply to you, 
contact Amy Gahran <A HREF="mailto:mtn@indra.com">mtn@indra.com</A> or phone (303) 440-8500. Thanks! 
