<A 
HREF="http://www.ncf.carleton.ca/freeport/social.services/eco/info/primer/wasgen/menu">Waste Generation</A> and
<A 
HREF="http://www.ncf.carleton.ca/freeport/social.services/eco/info/primer/wasred/menu">Waste Reduction.</A>
<DD>A series of Frequently Asked Questions files from Environment Canada.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.noraoil.com/">National Oil Recyclers Association</A>
<DD><P>
<HR width=80%>

<P>

