<HEAD>

<TITLE>EnvJourn Home Page: The Ozone Layer</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff">

<center><strong><em><A HREF = "env_home.htm">SEJ page top</A> | 
<A HREF = "env_srch.htm">Search this site</A> | 
<A HREF = "net_srch.htm">Search the Internet</A> | 
<A HREF = "mailto:clemings@cris.com">Comments</A></em></strong><br>
</CENTER>

<br>

<IMG ALT = "Society of Environmental Journalists logo" width=68 height=104 ALIGN = LEFT HSPACE  = 10 SRC  = "sej_half.gif">

<H1>Stratospheric Ozone Depletion<br></H1>

<br>
<br>
<br>

<HR>

<DL>

<DT><A HREF = "http://www.epa.gov/docs/ozone/index.html">
EPA's stratospheric ozone depletion page</a>
<P>

<DT><A HREF = 
"http://www.cs.ruu.nl/wais/html/na-dir/ozone-depletion/intro.html">
Stratospheric ozone depletion</A>
<DD>Frequently asked questions, by Robert Parson, Colorado State University.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.essential.org/orgs/Ozone_Action/">Ozone Action</A>
<DD>Home page of an environmental group working on this subject.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.unepie.org/ozonaction.html">United Nations
OzonAction Programme Home Page</A>
<DD>Includes a list of substances controlled under the Montreal Protocol, 
a detailed phaseout schedule, a newsletter, a schedule of ozone-protection 
events, a list of contacts, and links to other sites.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://sedac.ciesin.org/ozone/">Stratospheric Ozone
and Human Health Project</A>
<DD>From a NASA-designated data center, this site includes
ultraviolet dose climatology, a bibliographic database, 
thematic guides on ozone depletion's environmental and health
effects, and information on chlorofluorocarbons and ozone depletion.

<P> 

</DL>

<HR width=80%>

<P>

<center><strong><em><A HREF = "env_home.htm">SEJ page top</A> | 
<A HREF = "env_srch.htm">Search this site</A> | 
<A HREF = "net_srch.htm">Search the Internet</A> | 
<A HREF = "mailto:clemings@cris.com">Comments</A></em></strong><br>

<P>

Last revised Jan. 3, 1997
<A HREF = "mailto:clemings@cris.com">clemings@cris.com</a>

</CENTER>
