<br>

<HR>

<DL>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.lcv.org/">League of Conservation Voters</A>
<DD>Includes the league's annual scorecard for votes by members of Congress, plus the "Green Book," providing more detailed information on the environmental attitudes of each member.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.nrdc.org/nrdc/publ/breach.html">Breach of Faith</A>
<DD>Abstract of a Natural Resources Defense Council report on the Contract with America. See also <A HREF="http://www.nrdc.org/nrdc/field/state.html">State of Nature,</A> an NRDC update on current environmental legislation before Congress.
