<DD>Online access to annual reports and other documents filed by publicly traded companies.
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "http://www.ciit.org">Chemical Industry Institute of Toxicology</A>
<DD>Includes CIIT Impact (single-page summaries of CIIT toxicological
research with references to published literature).<br>
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.enviroindustry.com/">Environmental Industry Web Site</A>
<DD>Information about companies that offer environmental services or products, plus access to Internet-based resources for the environmental industry.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.portland.com/cee/">Center for Environmental Enterprise</A>
<DD>From Portland, Maine; it provides support for businesses that want to commercialize environmental technologies.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.uspto.gov">U.S. Patent Office</A>
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.epa.gov/docs/dfe">Cleaner Technologies for a Safer Future</A>
<DD>Home page for EPA's Designs for the Environment program.
<P>

</DL>


