SRC  = "sej_half.gif">

<H1>Other Internet Mailing Lists</H1>

<font size = +2>H</font>ere are listings of potentially interesting Internet mailing lists from the U.S. <A HREF="#epa">Environmental Protection Agency</A>, <A HREF="#envirolink">Envirolink</A> and the <A HREF="#igc">Institute for Global Communications</A> that aren't listed on the main <A HREF="env_list.htm">SEJ mailing lists page.</A>  Some may be public, some are private. Which are which? Beats us. Try subscribing and see, and <A HREF="mailto:clemings@cris.com">let us know</A> if you find something good.

<HR>
<A NAME="epa">
<H2>U.S. Environmental Protection Agency lists:</H2></A>
<DL>

<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">System Administrators</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe sysadm yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">Technical GIS</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe gistechs yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">ICEM Information Systems Workgroup</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe icem_info_serv yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">MERCURY mailing list</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe mercury yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">System and Network outages mailing list</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe outages yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">U.S. Mexican Border Discussions</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe us_mexborder yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
<DT><A HREF="mailto:listserver@unixmail.rtpnc.epa.gov">FRL XXXX-X</A><DD>To subscribe, send message reading only <EM>subscribe frl-xxxx-x yourfirstname yourlastname.</EM><BR>
