<A NAME="igc">
<H2>Institute for Global Communications lists</H2></A>

<FONT SIZE=+2>M</FONT>ajordomo@igc.apc.org serves the following lists. Some of these lists may be private. To subscribe, send an e-mail message to <A HREF="mailto:majordomo@igc.apc.org">majordomo@igc.apc.org</A>
with the words "subscribe (listname)" -- without the quotes, and substituting the name of the list to which you want to subscribe for the word (listname). To find out more about a list, send an e-mail message to <A HREF="mailto:majordomo@igc.apc.org">majordomo@igc.apc.org</A>
with the words "info (listname)" -- again without the quotes, and substituting the name of the list about which you want information for the word (listname).

