<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:LISTSERV@UNL.EDU">
listserv@unl.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Trickle-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Water-L
</strong><DD>Oriented toward water quality issues addressed by cooperative extensions.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:LISTPROC@LISTPROC.WSU.EDU">
listproc@listproc.wsu.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Water-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Water-on-line
</strong><DD>Covers water-related information found on the Internet.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:LISTPROC@UCDAVIS.EDU">
listproc@ucdavis.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Water-on-line yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

</DL>

<HR>

<A NAME = "journalism"><H3>Journalism lists:</h3></a>

<DL>
<strong><DT>Airwaves
</strong><DD>A daily digest of a newsgroup called rec.radio.broadcasting. A moderated
list, aimed at radio professionals.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:subscribe@airwaves.chi.il.us">
subscribe@airwaves.chi.il.us</a></em> with the word "subscribe" in the subject line and
nothing in the body of the e-mail message.

<strong><DT>CARR-L
</strong><DD>Discussion list for computer-assisted reporting and research.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:LISTSERV@ULKYVM.LOUISVILLE.EDU">
listserv@ulkyvm.louisville.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe CARR-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>CCR-L
</strong><DD>A discussion list for police and court beat reporters.<br>
To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:MAJORDOMO@reporters.net">
majordomo@reporters.net</a></em>
with <em>subscribe CCR-L</em> in the body of your e-mail message
and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Copyediting-L
</strong><DD>A list for copyeditors which includes lots of helpful tips
on grammar and sentence construction.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:listserv@cornell.edu">
listserv@cornell.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Copyediting-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Correx-l
</strong><DD>Discussion list for foreign correspondents.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:LISTSERV@dino.conicit.ve">
listserv@dino.conicit.ve</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Correx-l yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>FOI-L
</strong><DD>Freedom of information issues, the First Amendment and the public's right to know.
<br>To join, subscribe, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:listserv@suvm.syr.edu">
listserv@suvm.syr.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe FOI-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Freelance
</strong><DD>For independent journalists and
non-fiction writers who want to exchange information about how to
succeed as professional writers, obtain news and tips about emerging
markets for their work and exchange articles among each other and with
the public both for sale and for feedback/advice.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:owner-freelance@newshare.com">
owner-freelance@newshare.com</a></em> In the body of your e-mail message, 
include your name and address and a few words about your interests.

<strong><DT>Envj-L
</strong><DD>Discussion list of the International Federation of Environmental Journalists.<br>
To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:majordomo@mail.comlink.apc.org">
majordomo@mail.comlink.apc.org</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Envj-l</em> in the body of your e-mail message
and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>IRE-L
</strong><DD>Discussion of investigative reporting techniques.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:LISTSERV@MIZZOU1.MISSOURI.EDU">
listserv@mizzou1.missouri.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe IRE-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Journet
</strong><DD>Discussion list for journalism educators.
<br>To join, subscribe, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:LISTSERV@QUCDN.QUEENSU.CA">
listserv@qucdn.queensu.ca</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Journet yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>NewsLib
</strong><DD>Discussion list for news librarians, cybrarians, online researchers, media
archivists, mass media bibliographers, reporters and journalism educators.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@unc.edu">
listserv@unc.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe NewsLib yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>NICAR-L
</strong><DD>Discussion of how to do computer-assisted news.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:LISTSERV@MIZZOU1.MISSOURI.EDU">
listserv@mizzou1.missouri.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe NICAR-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>NPPA-L
</strong><DD>For the National Press Photographers
Association and visual communicators, news photographers and
editors, system operators and graphics editors.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@cmuvm.csv.cmich.edu">
listserv@cmuvm.csv.cmich.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe NPPA-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Online-News
</strong><DD>Discussion of online newspaper technology.
<br>To join, subscribe, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:online-news-request@marketplace.com">
online-news-request@marketplace.com</a></em>
with <em>subscribe online-news yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line. The list owner also asks you to include a line about your affiliation and/or interest.

<strong><DT>PRForum
</strong><DD>Discussion list for public relations professionals.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@indycms.iupui.edu">
listserv@indycms.iupui.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe PRForum yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Radio-L
</strong><DD>Digital audio broadcasting including technical info and 
the social and economic aspects of this new technology.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@vm1.spcs.umn.edu">
listserv@vm1.spcs.umn.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe PRForum yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Radio-Rider
</strong><DD>Discussions about computers, computing and show preparation. Frequented by
radio on-air personalities and others in broadcasting.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@radio-online.com">
listserv@radio-online.com</a></em>
with <em>subscribe radio-rider yourE-mailaddress</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>RTVJ-L
</strong><DD>Discussions by radio and television professors and students
about the trade, courses, equipment, and ethics.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listproc@listserv.umt.edu">
listproc@listserv.umt.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe RTVJ-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Scrnwrit
</strong><DD>Discussion list for screenwriters. Includes script outlines, info on
negotiations with agents, freelance fees and critiques of movies.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@tamvm1.tamu.edu">
listserv@tamvm1.tamu.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Scrnwrit yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Society of Environmental Journalists
</strong><DD>A discussion list for environmental journalism. Subscriptions open to 
<A HREF = "ENV_SEJ.HTM">SEJ</A> members only.<br>
To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF ="mailto:MAJORDOMO@indra.com">
majordomo@indra.com</a></em>
with <em>subscribe SEJ yourfirstname yourlastname <your e-mailaddress>
</em> in the body of your e-mail message
and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>SPJ-Online
</strong><DD>Discussion list run by the Society of Professional Journalists.
Includes SPJ chapter updates.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listserv@netcom.com">
listserv@netcom.com</a></em>
with <em>subscribe SPJ-Online</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.


<strong><DT>Stockphoto
</strong><DD>Discussions relating to stock photography.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:listproc@info.curtin.edu.au">
listproc@info.curtin.edu.au</a></em>
with <em>subscribe Stockphoto yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>VidPro-L
</strong><DD>A moderated list about video production, cinema studies and TV. Sometimes
includes job postings. Subscribers will be given a password.
<br>To join, send e-mail to:<em><A HREF = "mailto:LISTPROC@BGU.EDU">
listproc@bgu.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe VidPro-L yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the body of your e-mail message and nothing in the "Subject:" line.

<strong><DT>Writer-L
</strong><DD>Moderated discussions of feature writing, explanatory journalism, literary journalism and book journalism. Includes info on techniques, markets, jobs, agents and editors.
This list is associated with the Creative Nonfiction Project at the University of Oregon and is coordinated by two-time Pulitzer-prize winner Jon Franklin.
<br>To join, send e-mail to: <em><A HREF = "mailto:mailserv@oregon.uoregon.edu">
mailserv@oregon.uoregon.edu</a></em>
with <em>subscribe writer-l yourfirstname yourlastname</em> in the boyd of your e-mail
message. Also include a short bio of yourself.
</dl>
<HR>
