<H1>Wildlife<br></H1>

<br>
<br>

<HR>
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.fws.gov/search/fwrefser.html">Fish and Wildlife Reference Service</A>
<DD>A searchable database of more than 25,000 bibliographic citations dealing with fish and wildlife, maintained by the U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service. Requires a form-capable browser. 
First page contains instructions and a link to the query form. You can also search the FWS
headquarters phone directory and other databases from this site.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.fws.gov/laws/index.html">U.S. Wildlife Laws</A>
<DD>A collection from the U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service. Includes a summary of state wildlife laws as well as federal laws.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://curly.tec.army.mil/ugr/ugr.html">Stream Restoration Planning of Salmonid Habitat in Pacific Northwestern Watersheds</A>
<DD>
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.xmission.com/~gastown/herpmed/">Herpetology Hot Links</A>
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.aphis.usda.gov/adc/adchome.html">Animal Damage Control 
program,</A> U.S. Department of Agriculture.
<P>

