A Guide to Environmental Resources on the Internet</A>
<DD>by Carol Briggs-Erickson and Toni Murphy
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "ftp://una.hh.lib.umich.edu/inetdirsstacks/environment:phelps">
Selected Bibliography of Sources of Environmental Information on the Internet</A>
<DD>by Anda Phelps
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "ftp://una.hh.lib.umich.edu/inetdirsstacks/conservation:wendling">
Guide to Online Resources  for the Conservationist</A>
<DD>by Dan Wendling and J. Scott Christianson
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "ftp://una.hh.lib.umich.edu/inetdirsstacks/agri:drew">
A Guide to Internet/Bitnet Resources in  Agriculture and Related Sciences</A>
<DD>by Wilfred Drew
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "ftp://una.hh.lib.umich.edu/inetdirsstacks/biodivers:gordon">
International Biodiversity Information Available on the Internet Gopher System</A>
<DD>by Sean N. Gordon
<P>

