<H1>Canada</H1>

<br>
<br>
<br>

<HR width=80%>
<P>
<A HREF = "http://www.ec.gc.ca/">Environment Canada's "Green Lane"</A>
<UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.ns.ec.gc.ca/">Atlantic Region</A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.wul.qc.ec.gc.ca/envcan">Qu&eacute;bec Region</A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cciw.ca/green-lane/intro.html">Ontario Region</A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.mb.doe.ca/">Prairie &amp; Northern Region</A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.pwc.bc.doe.ca/">Pacific &amp; Yukon Region</A> 
