<H1>Public Lands<br></H1>

<br>
<br>
<br>

<HR>

<DL>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.blm.gov/">U.S. Bureau of Land Management</A>
<DD>Home page of the custodian of most public lands in the United States, except those held by the <A HREF="http://www.fs.fed.us/">Forest Service</A> and the <A HREF="http://www.nps.gov/">National Park Service.</A>
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.northernminer.com/">The Northern Miner</A>
<DD>Online edition of a Canadian newspaper covering the mining industry.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="gopher://gopher.igc.apc.org:70/11/environment/forests/western.lands">Econet Western Lands Gopher</A>
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://rohan.sdsu.edu/dept/serg/serg.html">Soil Ecology and Restoration Group</A>
<DD>From San Diego State University. Includes a data catalog for the Desert Lands Restoration Task Force.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://ranch.tamu.edu/rlem/">Department of Rangeland Ecology and Management, Texas A&M University</A>
<DD>
<P>

</DL>

