<H1>Environmental Journalism Associations and Newsletters</H1>

OK, so we're not exactly neutral on this subject. But we can't help pointing out 
that a membership in <A HREF = "ENV_SEJ.HTM">SEJ</A> gives you both the 
benefits of associating with our 1,100 other members (we have an <A HREF="sej_conf.htm">annual 
conference</A> in October -- this year it's in St. Louis) and a subscription to our 
quarterly <A HREF = "SEJOURN.HTM">SEJournal.</A> That's one reason 
we've listed ourselves first on this page. (Can you blame us?)

<HR>

<H3><strong><em>ASSOCIATIONS:</em></strong></H3>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF = "env_sej.htm">Society of Environmental Journalists</A><br>
(Membership is $35 per year; open to environmental journalists and related academicians.)<br>
P.O. Box 27280<br>
Philadelphia, PA 19118<br>
Phone: (215) 247-9710<br>
Fax: (215) 247-9712<br>
Internet: <A HREF = "mailto:sejoffice@aol.com">sejoffice@aol.com</A><br>
</UL>

<UL>
<LI><P><A HREF="ifej0306.htm">International Federation of Environmental Journalists</A><br>
Contact <A HREF = "mailto:sejoffice@aol.com">SEJ office</A> (above) or:<BR>
<A HREF = "mailto:detjen@pilot.msu.edu">Jim Detjen<BR></A>
Knight Chair of Environmental Journalism<BR>
Michigan State University<BR>
East Lansing, MI 48824-1212
Phone: (517) 355-5794
</UL>

<H3><strong><em>NEWSLETTERS:</em></strong></H3>

<UL>
<LI><em><A HREF = "EW.HTM">Environment Writer</A> </em><br>
($29 per year; free on request to accredited print and broadcast environmental journalists)<BR>
Environmental Health Center<BR>
National Safety Council<BR>
1019 19th St. NW ste. 401<BR>
Washington, DC 20036<BR>
Phone: (202) 293-2270<BR>
Fax: (202) 293-0032<BR>
Internet: <A HREF = "mailto:ehc@cais.com">ehc@cais.com</A><BR>
</UL>

<UL>
<LI><em>Environmental News Reporter</em><br>
($395 per year; targeted at corporate and agency media relations specialists)<br>
<A HREF="http://www.tjfr.com">TJFR Publishing Co.</A><br>
545 North Maple Ave.<br>
Ridgewood, NJ 07450<br>
Phone: (201) 444-6061<br>
Fax: (201) 444-5919<br>
Internet: <A HREF = "mailto:tjfr@tjfr.com">tjfr@tjfr.com</A><br>
</UL>

