<IMG ALT = SEJ LOGO ALIGN = LEFT HSPACE  = 10
SRC  = "sej_half.gif">

<H1>SEJournal<br>Winter 1995-96</H1>
<p>

<FONT SIZE=+2>P</FONT>ost-mortems on the Energy Department's public relations blowup, 
reviews of SEJ's 1995 national conference, and viewpoints on federal public lands are highlights
of this issue.</p>

