<H3><A NAME = "greenbeat">The Green Beat</A><BR>
</H3>
<P>
<EM>Contribute to Green Beat
<P>
The Green Beat is designed as an idea exchange for environmental
journalists and educators. It relies on information submitted
by reporters about important issues, outstanding coverage, and
developments in environmental education and the communications
profession on a state-by-state basis. 
<P>
To submit ideas or copies of series for possible mention in The
Green Beat, consult the following list and contact the SEJ correspondent
for the appropriate state(s). They are:<BR></EM>
