<H1>Hazardous<br>and Solid Wastes<BR></H1>

<br>

<HR>
<P>
<DL>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.epa.gov/enviro/html/ef_home.html">ENVIROFACTS</A>
<DD>Online access to five major EPA databases, including the Toxic Release Inventory, and databases associated with Suprfund and the Resource Conservation and Recovery Act.
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "http://atsdr1.atsdr.cdc.gov:8080/atsdrhome.html">Agency for Toxic Substances and Disease Registry</A>
<DD>HazDat: A database of contaminants found at Superfund sites, searchable by geographical area.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.epa.gov/superfnd/">Superfund Home Page</A>
<DD>Includes current status of Superfund reauthorization and budget proposals, regional contacts for program information, and EPA's response to criticisms of the program.
<P>

</DL>

