<HEAD>

<TITLE>EnvJourn Home Page: Global warming</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff">

<center><strong><em><A HREF = "env_home.htm">SEJ page top</A> | 
<A HREF = "env_srch.htm">Search this site</A> | 
<A HREF = "net_srch.htm">Search the Internet</A> | 
<A HREF = "mailto:clemings@cris.com">Comments</A></em></strong><br>
</CENTER>

<BR>

<IMG ALT = "Society of Environmental Journalists logo" width=68 height=104 ALIGN = LEFT HSPACE  = 10 SRC  = "sej_half.gif">

<H1>Global warming</H1>

<br>
<br>
<br>

<HR width=80%>

<DL>
<DT><A HREF="http://gcmd.gsfc.nasa.gov">NASA's Global Change Master Directory</A>
<DD>Descriptions of ecologic, hydrologic, meteorologic, oceanographic, geologic and global change data
held at federal agencies, universities and research centers in the U.S. and elsewhere. Direct links are 
provided when possible, and keyword and free-text search capabilities are included.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="gopher://pandora.sf.ca.us:8001/1ftp%3Aigc.apc.org@/pub/ECIX/">Energy and Climate Information Exchange (ECIX)</A>
<DD>Newsletters and other information on global warming, from Canada, the Netherlands and elsewhere.
<P>

<DT><A HREF = "http://pegasus.nesdis.noaa.gov/pathfinder.html">NOAA Atmospheric Pathfinder Program</A>
<DD>Data sets on global warming.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.globalchange.org/">Global Change</A>
<DD>Published by the Center for Global Change at the University of Maryland.
<P>

<DT><A HREF="http://www.epa.gov/docs/GCDOAR/Methane.html">EPA Methane Outreach Program</A>
<P>

</DL>

<HR width=80%>

<P>

<center><strong><em><A HREF = "env_home.htm">SEJ page top</A> | 
<A HREF = "env_srch.htm">Search this site</A> | 
<A HREF = "net_srch.htm">Search the Internet</A> | 
<A HREF = "mailto:clemings@cris.com">Comments</A></em></strong><br>

<P>

Last revised Jan. 3, 1997
<A HREF = "mailto:clemings@cris.com">clemings@cris.com</A>

