<head>
<title>District of Maple Ridge - Business</title>
<meta name="description" content="Maple Ridge, British Columbia,
             Your source for information on Maple Ridge!  Check out what Maple Ridge has to offer!">
<meta name="keywords" content="Maple Ridge, District of Maple Ridge,
             Pitt Meadows, Haney, British Columbia, Tourism, Business,
             Vacation, Holiday, Fraser Valley, Maple Ridge, Government,
             Lower Mainland, Mountains, Alouette, Golden Ears, Park, 
             Parks">
