<tr><td width=278><font size=2>Service Commercial Per Capita (m2) </font></td><td width=70><font size=2>1.75</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>1.75</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>1.75</font> </td><td width=70><font size=2>1.75</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>1.75</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>1.75</font> </td></tr>
<tr><td width=278><font size=2>5 Year Space Requirement (m2) </font></td><td width=70><font size=2>16,191 </font></td><td width=70><font size=2>18,769</font> </td><td width=70><font size=2>21,758</font> </td><td width=70><font size=2>25,225</font> </td><td width=70><font size=2>29,244</font> </td><td width=70></td></tr>
<tr><td width=278><font size=2>Annual Office Space Requirement (m2) </font></td><td width=70><font size=2>3,238</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>3,754</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>4,352</font> </td><td width=70><font size=2>5,045</font></td><td width=70><font size=2>5,849</font></td><td width=70></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p><font size=3><b>Retail Space</b></font><font size=4> <br>
</font><font size=3>Leasing rates in Maple Ridge vary, with higher rates at the large anchored shopping centres and lower rates for 
streetfront retail. Rates in anchored centres range between $18 and $25 per square foot (net) with tenant inducements 
between $10 and $20 per square foot and two to three months free rent. Streetfront buildings, on the other hand, 
demand rates between $10 and $12 per square foot (net) with inducements falling between $5 and $10 per square 
foot, including free rent.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=3>The vacancy rate is expected to continue on a downward trend in the near future, due to a lack of new spaces coming 
on stream. Figure 3 shows '93 and '94 vacancy rates in Maple Ridge compared with those of other Lower Mainland 
communities.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=center><font size=3><b>Figure 3 - Retail Vacancy Rates</b></font><font size=4> </font></p>
<div align=center><center>
<table border=1>
<tr><td width=197></td><td width=120><font size=2><b>09/93 </b></font></td><td width=120><font size=2><b>09/94</b></font> </td></tr>
<tr><td width=197></td><td width=120><font size=2><b>(%)</b></font> </td><td width=120><font size=2><b>(%)</b></font> </td></tr>
<tr><td width=197><font size=2>Coquitlam</font></td><td width=120><font size=2>3.40 </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>3.86</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=197><font size=2>Port Coquitlam </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>3.48 </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>3.32</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=197><font size=2>Port Moody</font></td><td width=120><font size=2>0.32 </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>2.82</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=197><font size=2>Maple Ridge </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>2.31 </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>2.18</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=197><font size=2>GVRD</font></td><td width=120><font size=2>3.33 </font></td><td width=120><font size=2>3.42</font></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
</td></tr>
