<font size=3><b><img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="location.html"><font size=3><b>Location</b></font></a><font size=3><b> <img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="climate.html"><font size=3><b>Climate</b></font></a><font size=3><b> <img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="ourneighbours.html"><font size=3><b>Our Neighbours<br>
<br>
</b></font></a><font size=3><b><img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="greetings.html"><font size=3><b>Greetings</b></font></a></td><td align=right valign=top><img src="welcome_main.gif" align=bottom width=126 height=121></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p align=left><strong>Maple Ridge... Land of Diversity<br>
</strong><font size=3>From pristine mountains to agricultural plains; from home businesses to lumber mills; from 
forest parkland to urban bustle - Maple Ridge presents a wealth of diversity while defying 
definition.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>We might attempt to define Maple Ridge by our location. Situated on the north shore of the 
Fraser River, we are an hour's drive from the heart of Vancouver, one of Canada's major 
commercial centres. Our climate is that of a temperate rain forest, with luxuriant vegetation 
and mild, moist winters. As a member community of the Greater Vancouver Regional 
District, we enjoy the advantages of proximity to a sophisticated urban centre, without the 
disadvantages of big-city life.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>But that's only part of the picture.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>We could also say that Maple Ridge is a wonderful place to enjoy nature. Our many parks 
and trails offer an unrivaled opportunity to enjoy the peaceful beauty of mountains, rivers 
and marshes - and it is all as close as the wind.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>And yet . . . .Maple Ridge is a fast-growing community. Like the Fraser River flowing 
swiftly past us to the south, there is a current of change urging us on, bringing new 
businesses to serve our expanding population, encouraging housing and commercial 
development to keep up with the needs of our residents.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>Anything else?</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>We could certainly call ourselves a family-oriented community. Our clean, modern schools 
offer quality education for children of all ages and abilities. Our many sports and recreation 
facilities provide opportunities for active, healthy fun. Annual community events such as 
First Night, Canada Day, Mountain Festival, and the Agricultural Fair give families and 
children a chance to grow, learn, and play.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>We might also say that Maple Ridge is the people who live here. Our recent population 
boom has brought a substantial skilled labour force to the community. Many of our 
residents commute to other areas of the Lower Mainland for employment, while enjoying 
the lifestyle advantages Maple Ridge offers. Businesses and industries locating in Maple 
Ridge find no shortage of qualified workers eager to fulfill their personnel requirements!</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>Or perhaps the ways in which we care for each other can help define Maple Ridge. 
Community social service agencies operate specialized programs and the Society for 
Friends in Need runs a food bank. With a modern hospital and extended care facilities, 
police, fire department, and other emergency and health care services, Maple Ridge is fully 
prepared to respond to people in need.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=left><font size=3>In the end it seems that Maple Ridge can't be narrowly defined. A combination of many fine 
qualities, it is a dynamic community with history and heart, where there is room to grow, 
lots to do, and people who care. This web site will give you in-depth insight into the 
outstanding features of Maple Ridge. So read on . . . and enjoy!</font><font size=4> </font></p>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
</body>

</html>

</DOC>
