<p><font size=3>Maple Ridge is big on community spirit, and we love to<br>
show it off at our many family-oriented celebrations.</font> </p>
</td><td align=right valign=top><img src="communityevents_main.jpg" align=bottom width=140 height=141></td></tr>
</table>
<p></p>
</center></div>
<div align=center><center>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=550>
<tr><td valign=top><font size=3><b>Maple Ridge Mountain Festival</b></font><font size=4><em><br>
</em></font><font size=3>The Mountain Festival, an annual event that takes place in May, 
starts off the year's festivities. This unique celebration allows 
community groups and organizations to tell the world who they are. 
Annual events include the Mountain Festival Parade, Dewdney 
Community Mile, Home Show, and Family Arts Fair.</font></td><td align=right valign=top><font size=3><b><img src="recgroup.gif" align=bottom width=141 height=116></b></font></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p><font size=3><br>
<b>Ridge Meadows Agricultural Fair</b></font><font size=4><em> <br>
</em></font><font size=3>The Agricultural Fair is an authentic old-fashioned country fair originating in 1901. Focusing 
on livestock displays, the fair is an opportunity for children to learn about animals' habits 
and care. The event also includes a petting zoo and a midway, as well as logging shows and 
entertainment for young and old to enjoy.<br>
<br>
<b>First Night</b><em><b><br>
</b></em>The annual New Year's Eve celebration in Maple Ridge is a drug and alcohol free Arts 
Festival, enjoyed by the whole community. This traditional celebration honours the creative 
spirit with performances, exhibitions, entertainment, and fun in unexpected places 
throughout downtown Maple Ridge.<br>
<br>
<b>Santa Claus Parade</b></font><font size=4><br>
</font><font size=3>Rain or shine, thousands of viewers turn out to enjoy Santa. Brightly decorated floats and 
entries from various businesses and organizations compete for prizes, but there's no 
competition for the most popular float!</font><font size=4> </font></p>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
