<html>

<head>
<title>District of Maple Ridge - Location</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#800000" vlink="#808080" alink="#FFFF00" topmargin="0" leftmargin="0" TOPMARGIN="0">
<div align=center><center>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=550>
<tr><td><p align=center><a href="home.html"><font size=2><img src="home.gif" alt="Home" align=bottom width=80 height=20></font></a><a href="tourism.html"><font size=2><img src="tourism_icon.gif" alt="Tourism" align=bottom width=88 height=20></font></a><a href="government.html"><font size=2><img src="government_icon.gif" alt="Government" align=bottom width=100 height=20></font></a><a href="business.html"><font size=2><img src="busines_icon.gif" alt="Business" align=bottom width=80 height=20></font></a><a href="localnews.html"><font size=2><img src="localnews_icon.gif" alt="Local News" align=bottom width=93 height=20></font></a><a href="contact.html"><font size=2><img src="Contact_icon.gif" alt="Contact" align=bottom width=79 height=20></font></a><font size=2> </font></p>
<div align=center><center>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=550>
<tr><td valign=top><font size=5><strong><u>Location</u></strong></font> &#149; <font size=4><u>District of Maple Ridge</u></font><br>
<br>
<font size=3><b><img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="welcome.html"><font size=3><b>Welcome</b></font></a><font size=3><b> <img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="climate.html"><font size=3><b>Climate</b></font></a><font size=3><b> <img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="ourneighbours.html"><font size=3><b>Our Neighbours</b></font></a></td><td align=right valign=top><img src="location_main.gif" align=bottom width=193 height=65></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p><font size=3>The District of Maple Ridge lies on the north shore of the Fraser River, 45 km east of the 
City of Vancouver. With the Coast Mountains standing guard to the north, and the Stave 
and Pitt Rivers forming our east and west boundaries, Maple Ridge is a community that 
combines small-town atmosphere with close proximity to a major trade centre.</font><font size=4><br>
<br>
</font><font size=3><b><img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> </b></font><a href="mapleridgemap.html"><font size=3><b>Map of Maple Ridge</b></font></a><font size=4><br>
*</font><font size=3><em>Other maps coming soon!</em></font> </p>
<p align=center><font size=2><b>Driving Distance to Selected Cities</b></font> </p>
