<p align=left><br>
<strong>Tax Analysis</strong><br>
Assessment Comparisons <br>
* Note: Properties are categorized into 9 different classes for assessment and taxation purposes. The 
Municipality of Maple Ridge has no properties within classes, 3 (Forestry), 4 (Machinery) and 7 (Tree 
Farm). <br>
<br>
Source: Municipal Finance Department - December 1995 </p>
