<DOCHDR>
http://district.maple-ridge.bc.ca:80/transportation.html 207.81.211.55 19970118230444 text/html 8668
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 18 Jan 1997 23:04:43 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
