<title>District of Maple Ridge - Industrial Development</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#800000" vlink="#808080" alink="#FFFF00" topmargin="0" leftmargin="0" TOPMARGIN="0">
<div align=center><center>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=550>
<tr><td valign=top><p align=center><a href="home.html"><font size=2><img src="government/../home.gif" alt="Home" align=bottom width=80 height=20></font></a><a href="tourism.html"><font size=2><img src="government/../tourism_icon.gif" alt="Tourism" align=bottom width=88 height=20></font></a><a href="government.html"><font size=2><img src="government/../government_icon.gif" alt="Government" align=bottom width=100 height=20></font></a><a href="business.html"><font size=2><img src="government/../busines_icon.gif" alt="Business" align=bottom width=80 height=20></font></a><a href="localnews.html"><font size=2><img src="government/../localnews_icon.gif" alt="Local News" align=bottom width=93 height=20></font></a><a href="contact.html"><font size=2><img src="government/../Contact_icon.gif" alt="Contact" align=bottom width=79 height=20></font></a><font size=2> </font></p>
<p><font size=5><strong><u>Industrial Development</u></strong><strong> </strong></font>&#149; <font size=4><u>District of Maple Ridge</u></font><br>
<br>
<font size=3>Maple Ridge has 272 net hectares of industrial zoned land. Figure 4 indicates the 
percentage of land situated in each of five industrial zones.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=3>Of the zoned land, 103 hectares are occupied and 169 are vacant. Vacant lands comprise 
49.7 hectares in Maple Meadows Business Park and 16 hectares in Albion Industrial Park, 
with Ruskin, Whonnock and Blue Mountain Industrial Parks accounting for the remaining 
vacant lands.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=center><font size=3><b>Figure 4 - Percentage of Total Industrial Area </b></font></p>
<div align=center><center>
<table width=500>
<tr><td valign=top width=50%><img src="indust_area_piechart.gif" align=bottom width=200 height=199></td><td width=50%><img src="indust_area_piechart1.jpg" align=bottom width=27 height=27> Maple Meadows Business Park<br>
<img src="indust_area_piechart2.jpg" align=bottom width=27 height=27> Ruskin<br>
<img src="indust_area_piechart4.jpg" align=bottom width=27 height=27> Whonnock<br>
<img src="indust_area_piechart5.jpg" align=bottom width=27 height=27> Blue Mountain<br>
<img src="indust_area_piechart3.jpg" align=bottom width=27 height=27> Albion</td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p><font size=3><b>Industrial Land Absorption<br>
</b>During 1989 to 1993, average annual industrial land absorption in all of Maple Ridge's 
industrial areas was 1.98 hectares. Industrial land absorption has been accelerating since 
1993, with 4.32 hectares absorbed in 1994 and 2.68 hectares in 1995.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=center><font size=3><b>Figure 5 - Industrial Land Absorption - 1985-1993 <br>
<br>
</b></font><img src="ind_land_absorb_graph.gif" align=bottom width=283 height=155> </p>
<p><font size=3><b>Maple Meadows Business Park<br>
</b>Maple Meadows, located in southwest Maple Ridge, has experienced significant activity 
during the last few years. Businesses located here include light and medium manufacturing, 
as well as high tech industry. The area is called a business park because of its top quality 
features: buildings with high office standards, building-design controls, and landscaping.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=3>Maple Meadows' development is planned in four phases. Figure 6 indicates the current 
status of each phase.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p align=center><font size=3><b>Figure 6 - Status of Land Development in Maple Meadows Business Park</b></font><font size=4> </font></p>
<div align=center><center>
<table border=1>
<tr><td width=148><font size=2><b>Maple Meadows</b></font> </td><td width=148><font size=2><b>Size (ha)</b></font> </td><td width=148><font size=2><b>Zoned </b></font></td><td width=148><font size=2><b>Vacant</b></font> </td></tr>
<tr><td width=148><font size=2>Phase I </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>12.31 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>12.31 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>0.00</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=148><font size=2>Phase II </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>26.57 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>11.61 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>5.00</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=148><font size=2>Phase III </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>53.05 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>13.77</font> </td><td width=148><font size=2>39.28</font> </td></tr>
<tr><td width=148><font size=2>Phase IV </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>2.88 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>0.00 </font></td><td width=148><font size=2>2.88</font></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p><font size=3><b>Albion Industrial Area</b></font><font size=4> <br>
</font><font size=3>This traditional industrial park, located in the south central part of Maple Ridge along the 
Fraser River, accommodates a wide spectrum of light and heavy industrial users. The area 
comprises 76 hectares of land that has been zoned for industrial use, of which 
approximately 16 hectares are vacant.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=3><b>Ruskin Industrial Area</b></font><font size=4> <br>
</font><font size=3>This site, primarily wood-related, is located in the eastern portion of Maple Ridge along the 
Fraser River. The total zoned area is 21 hectares, including 2.56 hectares of vacant land.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=3><b>Whonnock Industrial Area</b></font><font size=4> <br>
</font><font size=3>Also a wood-related site, the Whonnock Industrial Area is located along the Stave River in 
eastern Maple Ridge. The total zoned area is 37.5 hectares, with 27.72 hectares of vacant 
land.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=3>Future industrial activity is reserved for the Silver Valley area; approximately 350 hectares 
of vacant land are available in this northeastern section of Maple Ridge.</font><font size=4> </font></p>
<p><font size=4><b><u><img src="bulletleaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16></u></b></font><a href="municipal_services.html"><font size=4><b><u>Municipal Services</u></b></font></a><font size=4> </font></p>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
</body>

