sectors. The information and assistance this office provides serve the goals 
of promoting the growth of local industry, attracting new business and 
industry, and enhancing employment opportunities for residents of Maple 
Ridge. Services are available to investors, entrepreneurs, industry, and 
government.</font></td><td align=center valign=top><img src="anihorse.gif" align=bottom width=95 height=71><br>
