<table width=100%>
<tr><td align=center valign=top><img src="mayor.jpg" align=bottom width=149 height=181> </td><td valign=top width=400><p align=center><strong>Welcome to the Maple Ridge Homepage!</strong><br>
<br>
<strong>Mission Statement</strong><br>
<br>
<em>To promote a safe and livable community <br>
for our present and future citizens.</em><br>
</p>
<p>Maple Ridge is a growing, dynamic, and energetic community 
within the Greater Vancouver Regional District. We are proud of 
our heritage and the many natural assets of this area, from the 
Fraser River to the Coastal Mountain Range. </p>
</td></tr>
</table>
<p>As a Corporation, the District of Maple Ridge is committed to delivering quality services to 
our residents and customers. We are proud of our dedicated innovative workforce and 
strive to continuously improve our performance.<br>
<br>
I encourage you to explore our web site and please do not hesitate to contact us with 
comments, concerns, or questions.<br>
<br>
<em><strong>Mayor Carl Durksen</strong></em> </p>
<p>You can reach the Mayor at his office 463-5221<br>
or via e-mail at <img src="email_leaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16> <a href="mailto:carl_durksen@district.maple-ridge.bc.ca">carl_durksen@district.maple-ridge.bc.ca</a> <br>
Comments about the Maple Ridge site can be sent to:<a href="mailto:enquiries@district.maple-ridge.bc.ca"><br>
<img src="email_leaf.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=17 height=16> enquiries@district.maple-ridge.bc.ca</a> <br>
</p>
</td></tr>
</table>
