Municipality, Tom is responsible for the overall management of 
Operational Services, as well as coordination of that Division's 
activities with the other three Divisions. <br>
<br>
Tom joined the District of Maple Ridge in 1981. He is a graduate 
of the University of Manitoba, and before he came to the District 
he spent some time in the Air Force, worked as City Engineer in 
Trail, British Columbia, Municipal Engineer in the District of 
North Vancouver, and while with a consulting engineering 
company, spent several years in charge of a project in Malaysia.<br>
