Ridge and the District of Pitt Meadows as well as the 
maintenance of all District of Maple Ridge government properties 
(municipal buildings, rental properties). His responsibilities include 
the operation of all Municipal cemeteries. He holds the position of 
Director of Emergency Social Services for Maple Ridge/Pitt 
Meadows, is a Trustee of the Dyking District Road 13 and is Past 
President of the Meadow Ridge Rotary Club.<br>
