<tr><td valign=top colspan=3><em><b>Internal Factors</b></em></td></tr>
</table>
<p></p>
</center></div>
<div align=center><center>
<table border=1 cellpadding=4 cellspacing=1 width=526>
<tr><td valign=top width=64%><p align=center><font size=1><b>(O=Not Important, 1=Fairly Important, 2=Important, 3=Very 
