Maple Ridge Zone Amending By-law No. 5496-1996 <br>
second and third reading <br>
(to rezone from RS-2 (One Family Suburban Residential) to RS-1b (One Family Urban 
[medium density] Residential) to permit subdivision into approximately five lots).<br>
</p>
<p>04.02.02 <br>
Maple Ridge Official Community Plan Amending By-law No. 5497-1996<br>
second and third reading<br>
(to redesignate from Single Family Residential (15 units per net hectare) to Single Family 
Residential (18 units per net hectare). <br>
</p>
