</i></b></font><font size=2>The following reports have been dealt with at the Committee level and come forward based on the 
recommendations of the Committee. The Meetings are held concurrently on the Monday the week prior 
to this Council Meeting commencing at 2:00 p.m. in the Council Chamber and are open to the public.<br>
