(604) 467-7345 <br>
</b></font><b>Shelly Morrison, B.B.A., Clerk</b> <br>
<font size=2><b>(604) 463-5221, local 271 </b></font></p>
<p align=center><font size=4><b>Fax for above (604) 467-7331 </b></font></p>
<p align=center><b>Paul Henry, StoreKeeper II</b> <font size=2><b><br>
(604) 467-7361 <br>
</b></font><b>Al LaFrance, StoreKeeper I</b> <br>
<font size=2><b>(604) 463-5221, local 509</b></font> </p>
<p align=center><font size=4><b>Fax for above (604) 467-7360</b></font> </p>
<p align=center><b>e-mail Earl Oddstad at</b> <img src="email_leaf.gif" align=bottom width=17 height=16><a href="mailto:earl_oddstad@district.maple-ridge.bc.ca"><b>earl_oddstad@district.maple-ridge.bc.ca</b> </a><br>
