<body bgcolor="#ffffff">

<font face="HELVETICA,ARIAL">
<P><IMG SRC="http://128.164.161.15/nlcbar2.jpg" HEIGHT=40 WIDTH=277><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>
</FONT></FONT></P>

<P><IMG SRC="http://128.164.161.15/nlc350n.jpg" HSPACE=5 VSPACE=5 HEIGHT=252 WIDTH=350 ALIGN=RIGHT><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>
</FONT></FONT></P>

<H3><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>The Law School</FONT></FONT></H3>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Established in 1865. GW is
the oldest law school in the District of Columbia</FONT></FONT></P>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Home institution: The George
Washington University, founded in 1821 by charter of Congress</FONT></FONT></P>

<P>Other GW schools:<BR>
</P>

<UL>
<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.gwu.edu/~csas/">Columbian
School of Arts and Sciences </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>School of Medicine and Health
Sciences </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.seas.gwu.edu/">School
of Engineering and Applied Science </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.gwu.edu/~gsehd/">Graduate
School of Education and Human Development </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.sbpm.gwu.edu/">School
of Business and Public Management </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.gwu.edu/~elliott/">Elliott
School of International Affairs </A></FONT></FONT></LI>
</UL>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Location: On the main GW
campus in downtown Washington, D.C.</FONT></FONT></P>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Accreditation: Fully accredited
by the American Bar Association; Charter member of the Association of American
Law Schools</FONT></FONT><BR>
</P>

<H3><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Student Body</FONT></FONT>
<IMG SRC="http://128.164.161.15/great.jpg" ALIGN=RIGHT></H3>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Total approx. 1,750</FONT></FONT><BR>
</P>

<UL>
<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D. -- 1,496 (1,284 full-time,
212 part-time) </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>LL.M. -- 300 (from the U.S.
and approximately 25 foreign countries) </FONT></FONT></LI>
</UL>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>1996 J.D. Entering Class
Profile:</FONT></FONT><BR>
</P>

<UL>
<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Class size: 453 </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Geographic origin: 41 states,
D.C., Puerto Rico, the U.S. Virgin Islands, and six foreign countries </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Women: 45% </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Minorities: 30% </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Applicant pool: over 6,500
from more than 700 colleges and universities </FONT></FONT></LI>
</UL>

<H3><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Degree Programs</FONT></FONT></H3>

<UL>
<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-1.htm">J.D.</A>
full-time (three years); part-time (evening, four years) </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-2b.htm">LL.M.
in Environmental Law </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-2c.htm">LL.M.
in Government Procurement Law </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-2e.htm">LL.M.
in International and Comparative Law </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-2d.htm">LL.M.
in Intellectual Property Law </A></FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-2f.htm">General
LL.M.</A> </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-3a.htm">S.J.D.
in various fields</A> </FONT></FONT></LI>
</UL>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Joint degree programs:</FONT></FONT><BR>
</P>

<UL>
<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./Master of Business
Administration </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./Master of Public Administratiojn
</FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in International
Affairs </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in Science, Technology
and Public Policy </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in Security Policy
Studies </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in East Asian
Studies </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in Latin American
Studies </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in Russian and
East European Studies </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in European Studies
</FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./M.A. in International
Development Studies </FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>J.D./Master of Public Health
</FONT></FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>LL.M./Master of Public Health
</FONT></FONT></LI>
</UL>

<H3><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Curriculum</FONT></FONT></H3>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1>Over 200 <A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-1d.htm">elective
courses</A></FONT></FONT></P>

<P><FONT FACE="HELVETICA,ARIAL"><FONT SIZE=-1><A HREF="http://www.law.gwu.edu/5-1e.htm">Clinics:</A></FONT></FONT><BR>
