<html>
<head>
<TITLE>Full-Time Faculty and Deans</TITLE>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<font face="HELVETICA,ARIAL">
<H2>Full-Time Faculty and Deans</H2>

<p>
B<p>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="fac/BARRON.HTM">Jerome A. Barron</A>
<LI><A HREF="fac/BENITEZ.htm">Alberto M. Benitez</A>
<LI><A HREF="fac/BLOCK.htm">Cheryl D. Block</A>
<LI><A HREF="fac/BRAUNEI.htm">Robert Brauneis</A>
<LI><A HREF="fac/BUERG.htm">Thomas Buergenthal</A>
<LI><A HREF="fac/BUTLER.htm">Paul D. Butler</A>
</UL>

