<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<font face="HELVETICA,ARIAL">

<H3>Policies</H3>
       
For general office policies and procedures, students should refer to the most recent Student
Handbook.  Additional guidelines followed by the Career Development Office (CDO) are set by
The National Association for Law Placement (NALP).  Students and employers should become
familiar with the policies, procedures and guidelines set forth in the NALP Directory of Legal
Employers.  Failure to adhere to general office policies or NALP guidelines will result in a loss
of access to the resources of the CDO.  A copy of the Directory is available in the CDO
Resource Library at 2000 G. Street.


<H3><A HREF="http://www.gwu.edu/www/eeo.html">University Policy on Equal Opportunity</A></H3>



<p>
