<head>
<title>
Faculty Directory
Scott B. Pagel
</title>
</head>
<font face="HELVETICA,arial" size=-1>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<br>



<img src="http://128.164.161.15/s_pagel.gif" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=145>



<h3>
Scott B. Pagel
</h3><img src="http://128.164.161.15/yline.gif" width=357 height=17><p>
Director of the Law Library<BR> 
Associate Professor of Law<BR>
B.A., Michigan State University<BR> 
M.A.L.S., University of Michigan<BR> 
J.D., University of California, Berkeley<BR>
<p>
<p>


Professor Pagel has worked in academic law libraries since 1977. Before becoming director of the Jacob Burns Law Library in 1993, Professor Pagel was director of the law library and an associate professor at the University of Oklahoma. He has also served as the associate law librarian at Columbia Law School and as the 
public services librarian at Golden Gate University. He is active in the American Association of Law Libraries, and has 
written articles on law library management issues, legal bibliography, labor law research, and immigration law research.
<br>
</body>
</html>
</DOC>
