<center>
<h3>The George Washington University Law School</h3>
<h4>Fall 1996 Examination Schedule</h4>
</center>
<HR size=5 width=50% align=center>
<p>
ALL PROBLEMS WITH THE SCHEDULING OF EXAMS MUST BE CALLED TO THE
ATTENTION OF THE DEAN OF STUDENT AFFAIRS OFFICE (STOCKTON
104)
